-Minor spoilers-

This show is amazing. 

Matt Murdock was blinded as a young boy by a chemical spill in his eyes. His father was a boxer, who got shot and killed for not purposefully losing his match. Matt becomes a lawyer and fights crime with law during the day, and fights crime as a vigilante at night.

He's just a normal guy, who's also blind. (and of course had martial arts training) A must watch. Parental guidance suggested, as some episodes are very graphic, like someone's head getting smashed in by a car door and his brains falling out. Besides for the violence, 10 vigilantes/10